    "en": {
      "title": "A space for bicycles in front of supermarkets",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the current fuel crisis, many people have become accustomed to using bicycles. Many people can be seen traveling by bicycle in Colombo city.",
        "At present, bicycle parking facilities have been created near some supermarkets in Colombo.",
        "The photos show how bicycle parking facilities have been established in front of the 'Colombo City Center' located in Kompanjaveedi, Colombo, and how the people who came there have parked their bicycles."
